  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿嘿嘿，我们这儿还没完呢，我的朋友。不止这些类型的武器，你知道我不是在开玩笑，对吧？我真的想在这里考验你，我希望你明白。\n\n当然你会得到报酬！如果我让你白忙活一场，那我成什么人了。总之，我猜你想知道你现在需要做什么，好吧。再干掉一些目标，但这次你使用冲锋枪，我会给你清单，这些现在应该就够了。\n\n我有些备用弹药给你，记住这些武器穿透护甲的能力很差。所以注意你射击的位置，但像你这样训练有素的雇佣兵应该已经知道了，我想。",
    "en": "Hey hey hey, we're not done here my friend. There's more than just these types of weapons, you know that I wasn't joking with that, right? I really want to test you here, I hope you get that.\n\nOf course you'll be paid! Who would I be if you'd be left unrewarded for your troubles. Anyway, I assume you want to know what you need to do now, alright then. Take down a few more targets, but this time you use submachineguns, I will give you the list, these should do fine for now.\n\nI have some spare ammo for you, keep in mind that these weapons are terrible at getting through armor. So watch where you're shooting, but a trained mercenary like you already knows I suppose."
  },
